org.vadere.state.attributes.scenario

Class AttributesCar

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vadere.state.attributes.Attributes
      • org.vadere.state.attributes.scenario.AttributesScenarioElement
        • org.vadere.state.attributes.scenario.AttributesDynamicElement
          • org.vadere.state.attributes.scenario.AttributesAgent
            • org.vadere.state.attributes.scenario.AttributesCar

  • public class AttributesCar
extends AttributesAgent
    Class representing the attributes of a car scenario element. It inherits from the AttributesAgent class and is thus a dynamic moving scenario element for the simulation which contains all necessary properties to move over the simulation map.
